<h1 class="font-black text-center text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl break-normal">
  El dinero <span class="text-accent-500 dark:text-accent-dark-500"> sí compra</span> la felicidad.
</h1>

<label class="sr-only" for="search-posts">Buscar en posts</label>
<input id="search-posts" type="search" placeholder="🔍 Buscar en posts..." class="w-full px-4 py-2 rounded-full border-accent-500 dark:border-accent-dark-5 border-l-2 border-b-2 placeholder-accent-500 dark:placeholder-accent-dark-500 placeholder-opacity-100 my-8" />


<p class="opacity-75 my-4">Posts recientes ⏳</p>

{% set maxPosts = 3 %}
{% set postsList = collections.posts | head(-maxPosts) %}
{% set postsListCount = collections.postsAndBooks | length %}
<section class="flex flex-col my-8 space-y-4">
  {% for post in postsList | reverse %}
    {% include "postitem.njk" %}
  {% endfor %}  
</section>

<hr>

<p class="opacity-75 my-4">Lecciones de libros 📚</p>

{% set booksList = collections.books | head(-3) %}
{% set booksListCount = collections.books | length %}
<section class="flex flex-col my-8 space-y-4">
  {% for book in booksList | reverse %}
    <a class="no-underline hover:bg-accent-100 dark:hover:bg-foreground-dark p-4 rounded" href="{{ book.url | url }}">
      <h2 class="font-black text-accent-500 dark:text-accent-dark-500">{{ book.data.title }} </h2>
      <span class="text-sm opacity-75">Escrito por {{ book.data.author }}</span>
      <br>
      <time class="text-sm text-accent-600 dark:text-accent-dark-600" datetime="{{ book.data.published_at | htmlDateString }}">{{ book.data.published_at | readableDate }}</time> <span class="px-2 text-sm text-accent-600 dark:text-accent-dark-600">·</span> <span class="text-sm text-accent-600 dark:text-accent-dark-600">Lectura de {{ book | readingTime }}</span>  
      <p>{{ book.data.description }}</p>  
    </a>
  {% endfor %}
</section>

<a class="button block" href="/posts">Todos los posts 📂 ({{ postsListCount }})</a>

<section class="mt-8 mb-8 p-4 rounded-lg bg-accent-100 dark:bg-foreground-dark text-center">
  <h2 class="mb-4 text-center font-black">Actualizaciones <span class="text-accent-500 dark:text-accent-dark-500">perronas</span> 🐕 💌</h2>
  
  <ul>
    <li class="mb-4">Nudismo financiero 😳</li>
    <li class="mb-4">Historias personales, de éxito y fracaso 📈📉</li>
    <li class="mb-4">Opiniones de libros, apps y hechos modernos 📚📰</li>
    <li class="mb-4">Recursos para enriquecer la mente y la cartera 🧠💰</li>
    <li class="mb-4">Directo en tu correo 📬</li>
    <li class="font-black">Una vez por semana— Cero spam 🚫</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="animate-bounce text-4xl mt-4">👇🏼</div>

  <div data-id="substack-embed"></div>

  <p>Puedes revisar los <a href="https://perrodinero.substack.com/archive">correos anteriores aquí</a>, para que veas que están perrones.</p>
</section>

